960s. Also read Popper.
\par Won Exhibition to St John\rquote s College, Cambridge. Read English, loved writing: good models.
\par Went to hear Leavis for a term. Disliked his negative destructive style of lecturing. Did not like his answer to a question, which had hoped would lead to a dialogue. Preferred Tom Henn\rquote 
s oratorical lectures on Shakespeare. Important influence of Donald Davie, austere poet.
\par Became interested in sociology, but none in Cambridge. Read W.F. Whyte, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\langfenp1033\insrsid9441375\charrsid9441375 Street Corner Society}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
