idge friends reading anthropology, Jeremy Tunstall, Winston Fletcher. Sense that English not enough. Writing poetry himself since 14, edited issue of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
\i\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\langfenp1033\insrsid9441375\charrsid9441375 Granta}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\langfenp1033\insrsid9441375\charrsid9441375 
, thought of becoming a poet. Accepted for poetry course in California with Yvor Winters, with teaching assistantship. But girlfrien}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\langfenp1033\insrsid7738219 
