. Went to films together, beginning of this interest. She nudged him towards sociology. He left for four years in USA.
\par Awarded Knox Fellowship, Harvard. Took introductory courses in sociology, anthropology, psychology and Barrington Moore. Gained huge amount. Foundation courses structured and packaged, by comparison with lack of guidance at Cambridge. Intensive exposure t
o interesting material. Good lecturers, Barrington Moore, psychologist David McClelland on achievement, anthropologist Robert Rapapor}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\langfenp1033\insrsid7738219 
