\par Read Wylie, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\langfenp1033\insrsid9441375\charrsid9441375 Village in the Vaucluse}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
